column5: The Burnet Corridor is becoming more popular daily with all of the top rated restaurants, bars, and easy public transportation access. Our place, located in Brentwood, is a great launching pad for your Austin adventure, just a stones throw to quick public transit downtown. Walk to several bars including Lala's (famous Christmas bar), Yard Bar, Pour House, or Aristocrat and several top notch restaurants: Stubb's BBQ, Bufalina Due, Barley Swine, Flyrite, or Lick Honest Ice Creams!
